name: Orders placed in 2015
query:
SELECT account_id, occurred_at, quantity, amount_usd
FROM orders
WHERE occurred_at BETWEEN '2015-01-01' AND '2015-12-31'
GROUP BY account_id, occurred_at, quantity, amount_usd
HAVING quantity > 100
ORDER BY amount_usd DESC;
